quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Й“e falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,2,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e gomЙ—ini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immorЙ—o e Joomi maЙ“Й“e - O yawtanii Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O moЖҙЖҙinii fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on"
  47,3,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde yedduЙ“e Й“en jokkii meere nden, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e on. Ko wano nii Allah piyiranta yimЙ“e Й“en mise maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,4,"Si on arii hawrude e yedduЙ“e Й“en (ka hare), ko soppugol daaЙ—e Й—en. Haa si on Й—uЙ—Й—inii warugol Й“e, haЙ“Й“on koyЙ—e Й—en. Ko si on moЖҙЖҙoray e maЙ“Й“e accitugol Й“e Й“aawo Й—um, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare nden wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non Гұaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tun, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. WaraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en, pellet, O yeebataa golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,5,"Arma O fewna Й“e, O moЖҙЖҙina fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e"
  47,6,"O naadoya Й“e Aljanna, mo O anndini Й“e fii mun"
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on wonii wallooЙ“e fii Allah, O wallay on, O tabintina teppe mon Й—en"
  47,8,"YedduЙ“e Й“ee kan, halkaare woodanii Й“e, O majjinii kadi golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,9,"ЖҠum le ko tawde Й“e aГұii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,10,"E Й“ee yiilaaki e leydi ndin, Й“e teskoo ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii maЙ“Й“e. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  47,11,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde ko Allah woni giЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en; hara non yedduЙ“e Й“en, giЙ—o (woo) alanaa Й“e"
  47,12,"Pellet, Allah naadoyay gomЙ—imЙ“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й“en, Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata ley (kuЙ“eeje) majje. YedduЙ“e Й“en kan, hiЙ“e dakmitoo, Й“e Гұaamira wano neemoraaЙ—i Й—in Гұaamirta; hara non ko Yiite ngen woni jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e. @Corrected"
  47,13,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ca'e, Й“urnooЙ“e tiiЙ—ude cemmbe, e dii ndeen saare maa raЙ—iinde ma, Й“e Men halki, ballo alanaa Й“e"
  47,14,"Kere ko on wonЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mun, wa'i wa Й“en cuЙ—inanaaЙ“e kuuЙ—e mun bonЙ—e Й—en, Й“e jokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e"
  47,15,"Ko woni sifa Aljanna fodaaЙ—o on gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en: ina toon canЙ—i ndiyam Й—i dakamme mun waylaaki, e canЙ—i Й“ira Й—i waylataa dakamme mun, e canЙ—i konnjam welayЙ—am yarooЙ“e, e canЙ—i njuuri laЙ“Й“inaandi. Hino woodani Й“e kadi ton: kala dimЙ“e, e haforaneede immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. [ЖҒen wa'oyay] wa luttinoyteeeЙ“e Й“en ka Yiite, Й“e yarnee ndiyam fatayЙ—am, Й—am taЖҙa tetekki maЙ“Й“e Й—in"
  47,16,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e heЙ—itotooЙ“e ma. Kono ko haa si Й“e yaltii ka maaЙ—a, Й“e wi'ana okkaaЙ“e ganndal Й“en: \"Ko honЙ—um dee, o wi'unoo naanen?\" Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah noti e Й“erЙ—e mun Й—en, Й“e jokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,17,"FeewuЙ“e Й“en kan, O Й“eydu Й“e peewal O okkiЙ“e gomЙ—al maЙ“Й“e"
  47,18,"Hara Й“ee no habbii si wanaa Darngal ngal nde ardata Й“e e juhal? GomЙ—ii le maandeeji maggal arii. Ko honno Й“e waajitoroyta, si ngal ardanii Й“e (juhal)"
  47,19,"Awa anndu pellet, reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Allah, insinanoЙ—aa junuubi maa Й—in, e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en. Allah no anndi Гұallirde mon e hiirirde mon"
  47,20,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en hino wi'a: \"Hara nun cortewol (hare) jippotono!\" Si tawii le cortewol ГұeГұaangol jippinaama, fii hare jantaama e maggol, a tinay Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mun hino ndaare, ndaarЙ—e mo maayde faЙ—Й—ini. Ko haanannoo Й“e"
  47,21,"ko Й—oftagol e konngol moЖҙЖҙol. Si fiyaaku on fellitii, hara nun Й“e gomЙ—inno Allah, ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e"
  47,22,"E on tamЖҙinaaki, si wonii on Й—uurnike, nde bonnoton e leydi ndin, taЖҙon enЙ—amaaji mon"
  47,23,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah huЙ—i Й“en, O faaЙ—ini Й“e, O wumini giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,24,"E Й“ee tasktaako Alqur'aana, kaa ko sokirЙ—e woni woni e Й“erЙ—e mum en"
  47,25,"Pellet, Й“en ruttorЙ“e Й“abbe mun Й“aawo nde peewal ngal Й“anngannoo Й“e, ko seytaane cuЙ—inani Й“e, o hodi Й“e"
  47,26,"Ko tawde Й“e wi'anii Й“en aГұuЙ“e ko Allah jippini kon: \"Men Й—oftoto on e yoga e piiji\". Allah non no anndi gunndooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in"
  47,27,"Ko honno (Й“ee wa'oyta) tuma nde Malaa'ika'en timmini fii maЙ“Й“e, hara hiЙ“e bantoo geece maЙ“Й“e e dote maЙ“Й“e"
  47,28,"Ko tawde ko Й“e jokkii ko tikkinta Allah, Й“e aГұii welayЙ—i Mo Й—in, O bonni fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,29,Kaa Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mun sikuu wonnde Allah yaltintaa ngaynguuji maЙ“Й“e
  47,30,"Sinno Men haajuno, Men holleteno Й“e. Anndiraa Й“e maandeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in; ko pellet, a anndirayno Й“e ka konngol welngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon Й—en"
  47,31,"Ma Men jarribo on, haa Men annda tiiЙ—niiЙ“e Й“en e mon, e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en. Men jarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon"
  47,32,"Pellet, yedduЙ“e Й“en Й“e faddi laawol Allah ngol, Й“e lunndii NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde peewal ngal Й“anngannde Й“e, Й“en lorrataa Allah hay huunde. Ma O bonnu fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,33,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e! ЖҠoftee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on, wata on bonnu golle mon Й—en"
  47,34,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti Й“e maayi ko Й“e heeferЙ“e, Allah haforanoytaa Й“e"
  47,35,"Wata on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni fooluЙ“e Й“en, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njoЙ“di golle mon Й—en"
  47,36,"Anndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbeleeЙ—e tan; hara le si on gomЙ—iii, on hulii [Allah], O yeЙ—ay on njoЙ“di mon ndin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon Й—en"
  47,37,"Si O aru lamndaade on fii majje, haa O duГұii on (e mun), wuddon, O feГұГұina non konnaagu mon ngun"
  47,38,"Hey mon onon Й—oo, hiЙ—o noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wuddayЙ“e. Kala non wudduЙ—o, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon wonЙ—on waasuЙ“e Й“en. Si on huccii, O waЙ—titira on woЙ—Й“e goo, hara non Й“en wa'ataa wano mon"